Nicki Micheaux https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicki_Micheaux 0 Nicole "Nicki" Micheaux (born c. 1971) is an American actress, known for her role as Jennifer 'Jenn' Sutton in the ABC Family drama series Lincoln Heights (2007–2009), for which she received two NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Actress in a Drama Series nominations.
